    "\n",
    "Here, we attempt to reverse-engineer an input that maximally activates a given appliance channel. If successful, this could be seen as a **white-box model inversion attack**, where an adversary can understand what signals the model is looking for, and from there even attempt map the signal to known energy signatures of common appliances. "
